comments.body:
Hard to judge from far how the `image not known` errors occur.

@bmaupin, did you manually remove data from the storage or did those errors occur without manual intervention? Could you share the output of `podman --log-level=debug images`?

This might aid in pointing to the right direction. In the meantime, I'll open a PR for c/storage to include the image ID in the `image not known` error - it could be that another image isn't known when checking it a given image is a parent of another.
